The Orange Farm community has been left reeling after a spate of deaths. Three people have died in the area since Sunday. Community members say they now fear for their safety. eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu is following this story. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - A total of 43 people were murdered, children among them, in the last three months in Orange Farm. A further three women were found murdered in the last two weeks. Watch the video above for more details on this story.